  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ViewableBeam
    A laser beam that is drawn in a straight line.
    ViewableDoor
    A door that can be viewed and can change how open it is
    ViewableNonStationary
    An object that can be viewed, but may not look the same (position, rotation, elevation) from frame to frame.
    ViewableObject
    A nobject that can be viewed in the renderer
    ViewableOpenable
    A container that can be in an open or closed state
    ViewablePlayer
    A (human controller) player that can be viewed
    ViewableRoom
    A room that can be viewed.
    ViewableStationary
    An object that can be viewed and can be guaranteed to look the same (position, rotation, elevation) from frame to frame.
    ViewableWall
    A wall that can be viewed.
    ViewableWorld
    A world consisting of viewable rooms
